title: India 30 Year bond-Yield
description: India 30 Year Bond Yield was 7.58 percent on Monday November 7, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the India 30 Year bond-Yield reached an all time high of 9.92 in July of 2008. This page includes a chart with historical data for India 30Y.
